&lt;li&gt;Graph data structure: &lt;a rel=&quot;external&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;en.wikipedia.org&#x2F;wiki&#x2F;Graph_(abstract_data_type)&quot;&gt;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;en.wikipedia.org&#x2F;wiki&#x2F;Graph_(abstract_data_type)&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
